metadata.name: The Lover
metadata.description: It is beautiful to love as a woman. Each individually enchanting in her own way, conjuring a legacy of lovemaking in her wake. Generations of memories are passed down to us in the form of stories. Much of what is told no longer relevant as we are different individuals living in different times. Still, there is splendor in how each woman yearned, tried, succeeded or failed yet did not give up on love.Leaving behind the tale of how she bewitched her beloved.
